images.alt: A traditional Japanese ukiyo-e woodblock print featuring geishas with large, sparkling anime eyes and elaborate Sailor Moon-inspired twin buns and flowing hair ribbons, standing gracefully beneath cascading cherry blossoms. The cherry petals fall in distinct animation-style frames, each one rendered with bold black outlines and flat color fills typical of woodblock printing technique. Mount Fuji looms in the background with a gentle, smiling face reminiscent of Studio Ghibli forest spirits, while stylized ukiyo-e waves in the foreground contain tiny hidden cartoon characters nestled within their curling foam. The composition follows a vertical tate-e scroll format with visible wood grain texture, using warm sakura pinks contrasted against cool indigo blues, creating an elegant fusion of classical Japanese art and contemporary kawaii culture.
